Author: tranduchai
Title: ClassyCoin
Body: good project. Imagine a fully decentralized social network, where all the data and content is stored on the blockchain instead of centralized servers, and all the power lies with the users; not some individual nerd or company. Classy Network is one such step in the direction to get the users a platform that is not only powered by them but actually owned by them. It is the new generation decentralized social networking platform which is based on the ethereum blockchain for global connectivity and community building. Classy Network integrates peer to peer payment system and end to end fully encrypted features with no possibility of third party control of the data and zero possibility of downtime. Being an on-chain platform (Blockchain based), all of the user content would be lying on the blockchain instead of centralized servers. The platform allows you to communicate with friends and family in multiple unique ways, while providing state-of-the-art security and privacy.

Author: djy8206
Title: ClassyCoin
Body: Classy Coin‚Ä¨ is a high value, peer to peer decentralized digital currency that is based on the ERC20 token and deployed on the Ethereum blockchain. It is a cryptocurrency of the same nature as Bitcoin and Ethereum, but with a much bigger aim to specifically serve and help the Social Networking Industry. The coin is intended to be used within Classy Network to buy ad spaces, pay for goods and services and give tips to friends and families across the Classy Network. At Classy Network, we believe in supporting community building and social interaction with cryptocurrency rewards. For inspiring participation in the community, ClassyCoin would be presenting the users with a currency or a free market economy that is a fair accounting system, and consistently reflects each person's contribution. ClassyCoin aims to accurately and transparently reward an unbounded number of individuals who make subjective contributions to its community. We are taking appropriate steps to give people a real alternative and choice to connect with their loves one and be in full control of their data. Considering that, we have taken a revolutionary step of creating a blockchain based social networking platform.   Background  https://image.prntscr.com/image/A31ODmgbRm6Be8reAICEyQ.png  Social media have become ubiquitous and are playing an increasingly critical role in society. The wide use of social media platforms has generated massive user generated contents (UGCs). Research reveals that there are 2.5 billion active users of social networking sites, who collectively generate content having worth more than billions of dollars‚Äô. ClassyCoin is created based on idea of supporting social media and online communities by returning much of its value to the people who provide valuable contributions by rewarding them with cryptocurrency, and through this process create a currency that is able to reach a broad market, including people who have yet to participate in any cryptocurrency economy.   Introduction to Classy Social Network  Imagine a fully decentralized social network, where all the data and content is stored on the blockchain instead of centralized servers, and all the power lies with the users; not some individual nerd or company. Classy Network is one such step in the direction to get the users a platform that is not only powered by them but actually owned by them. It is the new generation decentralized social networking platform which is based on the ethereum blockchain for global connectivity and community building. Classy Network integrates peer to peer payment system and end to end fully encrypted features with no possibility of third party control of the data and zero possibility of downtime. Being an on-chain platform (Blockchain based), all of the user content would be lying on the blockchain instead of centralized servers. The platform allows you to communicate with friends and family in multiple unique ways, while providing state-of-the-art security and privacy.  https://image.prntscr.com/image/zEBIC59aSP2qs3B0TetmnA.png  Classy Network is backed by ClassyCoin- a cryptocurrency designed to be used for buying goods and services, purchase ad spaces from the integrated ad platform, donating to crowd funding campaigns, giving tips to friends and families across the network. Here is a brief description of the features that would be integrated into the Classy Network and would change your perception of what can be achieved through social media networks.   Classy Social Network Functionalities  https://image.prntscr.com/image/sBTjA8BSTgOWqFmezxriLw.png  1.VPN Social App Classy Network will be powered by a special VPN Social app. The app will facilitate both the mobile version of the network and also the desktop version to offer extreme browsing privacy. 2.YouTube integrated Classy Network would come with YouTube integrated which is the world‚Äôs biggest video sharing platform. This way users would be able to not only view the billions of video available directly in their feed but share them as well and get a fair reward for each impression, view and click.   Besides, this would also enable the network to avoid glitches being faced in the video content e.g. the current glitch of getting the app hanged while a video is being played on facebook.   3.Peer to Peer Payment Peer-to-peer payment system are electronic money transfers made from one person to another through an intermediary, typically referred to as a P2P payment application. P2P payments can be sent and received via mobile device or any home computer with access to the Internet, offering a convenient alternative to traditional payment methods. Classy Network has the built in functionality of peer to peer payment that would facilitates the users to send and receive their earned amount directly into their e-wallets without having to worry about massive surcharges implemented on traditional payment methods. 4.Marketplace Integrated Classy Network incorporates all of the e-commerce functions. It will allow you to create product Post for a specific product or service. Your friends, family or followers would see your post and would be able to purchase or bit directly. 5.Classy Network Mobile Apps Classy Network will be available both in the iOS and Android version. The mobile apps are being designed in a manner to support all features of the web version as well. Users would be able to chat, post, share, like and gets real time notification.   6.Instant Hollywood News and Updates For all Cinema lovers out there, Classy Network would allow you to get the latest updates from the world of Hollywood instantly. You would be able to watch and share videos related to Hollywood and keep yourself updated about the newest trends in the world of fashion. 7.News Publisher The Classy Network also comes integrated with the custom functionality of supporting news publishing. You would be able to view, publish and share news instantly and keep updated about whatever interest you have. 8.Listings Service Classy Network sports a listing service with the aim to provide accurate and structured data about properties for sale. The listing service would maintain a mechanism for listing brokers to offer compensation to buyer brokers who bring a buyer for their listed property without any service fee. 9.Personalized blog Instead of creating a separate blog on sites such as Wordpress.com or other, ClassyCoin comes integrated with Personalized Blog functionality. Unlike the current social networking platforms which mainly provide users with the facility of posts, Classy Network let the user create a personalized blog supported by a variety of custom functionalities such as different fonts and custom designs. The user also has the facility to view, like and share other users‚Äô blogs as well.   10.Complete Decentralized On-Chain Classy Network would be a completely decentralized on-chain platform that would allow users not to worry about a single centralized authority controlling the entire network. Instead it will be the community who will be the actual owner of the platform. All of the application data, user data and multimedia uploads will be stored on the blockchain. 11.Privacy Classy Network is a community driver project whose main focus is the privacy of our community and its data. Powered by ethereum smart contract blockchain technology, all of the data is distributed on a ledger without any single point of focus or failure.  Every single feature inside the network is end to end fully encrypted, which make it impossible for any third party to access your data.  WHITEPAPER http://www.classycoin.io/pdf/final_update_paper.pdf  CLASSYCOIN ROADMAP    Phase 1 Development 2015-2016  Website development started 2015  Android app development Started 2016 iOS app development started  Phase 2 Crowd Funding from March to April 2018  March 5, 2018  (at 10:00 GMT) to April 3rd, 2018 (at 10:00 GMT) ICO  April 2018 Classy Coin start trading on major decentralized exchanges  March 2018 Hire 6 more developers and 2 designer and increase our development team to 8 developers and 3 designers.  Phase 3 Launching the Network 2018 Q2-2019 Q2 2018 The release of Classy Social Network website  Q2 2018 The release of iOS app (beta version)  Q2 2018 The release of android app (beta version)  Q3 2018 The release of full website  Q3 2018 The release of full iOs app  Q3 2018 The release of full android app  Q3 2018 Classy Coin is fully integrated as a payment method on Classy Social Network  Q3 2018 Hotel Booking functionality is fully implemented in Classy Social Network  Q3 2018 Flight booking functionality is fully implemented in Classy Social Network  Q3 2018 Car Hire services is fully implemented in Classy social networking platform  Q3 2018 Listings services is fully implemented in Classy social network platform.  Q4 2018 The release of iOS and android VPN application   Important Contract Information Name: ClassyCoin Symbol: ClassyCoin Decimals:16 Contract Address: 0x30cc0e266cf33b8eac6a99cbd98e39b890cfd69b Maximum Supply (hard cap) - 100,000,000 ClassyCoin Emission rate - No new coins will ever be created Role of Coin/Token - used to buy Goods, Services and Ad spaces on Classy Network Available for puchase-70,000,000 ClassyCoin   ICO INFORMATION Accepted Currency - ETH Only Minimum Transaction Amount - 0.1 ETH ICO start on March 5, 2018 (at 10:00 GMT) and will run until April 3rd, 2018 (at 10:00 GMT) or when the maximum cap is reached. Coin Distribution - Contract will distribute tokens at the end of ICO The soft cap of this Token Sale is 20 Million ClassyCoin  Official Links Website: http://www.classycoin.io Telegram: https://t.me/joinchat/E7bGkULR97-OrNjgT7QaMQ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ClassyCoinCurrency/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/classycoin [/quote]

Besides, this would also enable the network to avoid glitches being faced in the video content e.g. the current glitch of getting the app hanged while a video is being played on facebook.   3.Peer to Peer Payment Peer-to-peer payment system are electronic money transfers made from one person to another through an intermediary, typically referred to as a P2P payment application. P2P payments can be sent and received via mobile device or any home computer with access to the Internet, offering a convenient alternative to traditional payment methods. Classy Network has the built in functionality of peer to peer payment that would facilitates the users to send and receive their earned amount directly into their e-wallets without having to worry about massive surcharges implemented on traditional payment methods. 4.Marketplace Integrated Classy Network incorporates all of the e-commerce functions. It will allow you to create product Post for a specific product or service. Your friends, family or followers would see your post and would be able to purchase or bit directly. 5.Classy Network Mobile Apps Classy Network will be available both in the iOS and Android version. The mobile apps are being designed in a manner to support all features of the web version as well. Users would be able to chat, post, share, like and gets real time notification.   6.Instant Hollywood News and Updates For all Cinema lovers out there, Classy Network would allow you to get the latest updates from the world of Hollywood instantly. You would be able to watch and share videos related to Hollywood and keep yourself updated about the newest trends in the world of fashion. 7.News Publisher The Classy Network also comes integrated with the custom functionality of supporting news publishing. You would be able to view, publish and share news instantly and keep updated about whatever interest you have. 8.Listings Service Classy Network sports a listing service with the aim to provide accurate and structured data about properties for sale. The listing service would maintain a mechanism for listing brokers to offer compensation to buyer brokers who bring a buyer for their listed property without any service fee. 9.Personalized blog Instead of creating a separate blog on sites such as Wordpress.com or other, ClassyCoin comes integrated with Personalized Blog functionality. Unlike the current social networking platforms which mainly provide users with the facility of posts, Classy Network let the user create a personalized blog supported by a variety of custom functionalities such as different fonts and custom designs. The user also has the facility to view, like and share other users‚Äô blogs as well.   10.Complete Decentralized On-Chain Classy Network would be a completely decentralized on-chain platform that would allow users not to worry about a single centralized authority controlling the entire network. Instead it will be the community who will be the actual owner of the platform. All of the application data, user data and multimedia uploads will be stored on the blockchain. 11.Privacy Classy Network is a community driver project whose main focus is the privacy of our community and its data. Powered by ethereum smart contract blockchain technology, all of the data is distributed on a ledger without any single point of focus or failure.  Every single feature inside the network is end to end fully encrypted, which make it impossible for any third party to access your data. Author: Jain01
Title: ClassyCoin
Body: Hi, After reading whole project this project is very interesting idea of crypto industry. Best part is to focus on social Networking industry to connect peer to peer. This will  develop  in future like bitcoin and ethereum. I am very happy To be part of it. quote author=ClassyCoin link=topic=2380307.msg24308359#msg24308359 date=1510253509] Welcome to the New Beginning in Social Networking Industry  https://image.prntscr.com/image/OzfnoRaiQ9Gluxx4nr2nUw.jpg  Classy Coin‚Ä¨ is a high value, peer to peer decentralized digital currency that is based on the ERC20 token and deployed on the Ethereum blockchain. It is a cryptocurrency of the same nature as Bitcoin and Ethereum, but with a much bigger aim to specifically serve and help the Social Networking Industry. The coin is intended to be used within Classy Network to buy ad spaces, pay for goods and services and give tips to friends and families across the Classy Network. At Classy Network, we believe in supporting community building and social interaction with cryptocurrency rewards. For inspiring participation in the community, ClassyCoin would be presenting the users with a currency or a free market economy that is a fair accounting system, and consistently reflects each person's contribution. ClassyCoin aims to accurately and transparently reward an unbounded number of individuals who make subjective contributions to its community. We are taking appropriate steps to give people a real alternative and choice to connect with their loves one and be in full control of their data. Considering that, we have taken a revolutionary step of creating a blockchain based social networking platform.   Background  https://image.prntscr.com/image/A31ODmgbRm6Be8reAICEyQ.png  Social media have become ubiquitous and are playing an increasingly critical role in society. The wide use of social media platforms has generated massive user generated contents (UGCs). Research reveals that there are 2.5 billion active users of social networking sites, who collectively generate content having worth more than billions of dollars‚Äô. ClassyCoin is created based on idea of supporting social media and online communities by returning much of its value to the people who provide valuable contributions by rewarding them with cryptocurrency, and through this process create a currency that is able to reach a broad market, including people who have yet to participate in any cryptocurrency economy.   Introduction to Classy Social Network  Imagine a fully decentralized social network, where all the data and content is stored on the blockchain instead of centralized servers, and all the power lies with the users; not some individual nerd or company. Classy Network is one such step in the direction to get the users a platform that is not only powered by them but actually owned by them. It is the new generation decentralized social networking platform which is based on the ethereum blockchain for global connectivity and community building. Classy Network integrates peer to peer payment system and end to end fully encrypted features with no possibility of third party control of the data and zero possibility of downtime. Being an on-chain platform (Blockchain based), all of the user content would be lying on the blockchain instead of centralized servers. The platform allows you to communicate with friends and family in multiple unique ways, while providing state-of-the-art security and privacy.  https://image.prntscr.com/image/zEBIC59aSP2qs3B0TetmnA.png  Classy Network is backed by ClassyCoin- a cryptocurrency designed to be used for buying goods and services, purchase ad spaces from the integrated ad platform, donating to crowd funding campaigns, giving tips to friends and families across the network. Here is a brief description of the features that would be integrated into the Classy Network and would change your perception of what can be achieved through social media networks.   Classy Social Network Functionalities  https://image.prntscr.com/image/sBTjA8BSTgOWqFmezxriLw.png  1.VPN Social App Classy Network will be powered by a special VPN Social app. The app will facilitate both the mobile version of the network and also the desktop version to offer extreme browsing privacy. 2.YouTube integrated Classy Network would come with YouTube integrated which is the world‚Äôs biggest video sharing platform. This way users would be able to not only view the billions of video available directly in their feed but share them as well and get a fair reward for each impression, view and click.   Besides, this would also enable the network to avoid glitches being faced in the video content e.g. the current glitch of getting the app hanged while a video is being played on facebook.   3.Peer to Peer Payment Peer-to-peer payment system are electronic money transfers made from one person to another through an intermediary, typically referred to as a P2P payment application. P2P payments can be sent and received via mobile device or any home computer with access to the Internet, offering a convenient alternative to traditional payment methods. Classy Network has the built in functionality of peer to peer payment that would facilitates the users to send and receive their earned amount directly into their e-wallets without having to worry about massive surcharges implemented on traditional payment methods. 4.Marketplace Integrated Classy Network incorporates all of the e-commerce functions. It will allow you to create product Post for a specific product or service. Your friends, family or followers would see your post and would be able to purchase or bit directly. 5.Classy Network Mobile Apps Classy Network will be available both in the iOS and Android version. The mobile apps are being designed in a manner to support all features of the web version as well. Users would be able to chat, post, share, like and gets real time notification.   6.Instant Hollywood News and Updates For all Cinema lovers out there, Classy Network would allow you to get the latest updates from the world of Hollywood instantly. You would be able to watch and share videos related to Hollywood and keep yourself updated about the newest trends in the world of fashion. 7.News Publisher The Classy Network also comes integrated with the custom functionality of supporting news publishing. You would be able to view, publish and share news instantly and keep updated about whatever interest you have. 8.Listings Service Classy Network sports a listing service with the aim to provide accurate and structured data about properties for sale. The listing service would maintain a mechanism for listing brokers to offer compensation to buyer brokers who bring a buyer for their listed property without any service fee. 9.Personalized blog Instead of creating a separate blog on sites such as Wordpress.com or other, ClassyCoin comes integrated with Personalized Blog functionality. Unlike the current social networking platforms which mainly provide users with the facility of posts, Classy Network let the user create a personalized blog supported by a variety of custom functionalities such as different fonts and custom designs. The user also has the facility to view, like and share other users‚Äô blogs as well.   10.Complete Decentralized On-Chain Classy Network would be a completely decentralized on-chain platform that would allow users not to worry about a single centralized authority controlling the entire network. Instead it will be the community who will be the actual owner of the platform. All of the application data, user data and multimedia uploads will be stored on the blockchain. 11.Privacy Classy Network is a community driver project whose main focus is the privacy of our community and its data. Powered by ethereum smart contract blockchain technology, all of the data is distributed on a ledger without any single point of focus or failure.  Every single feature inside the network is end to end fully encrypted, which make it impossible for any third party to access your data.  WHITEPAPER http://www.classycoin.io/pdf/final_update_paper.pdf  CLASSYCOIN ROADMAP  https://image.prntscr.com/image/GqObnP5tS3SK8iHg5bXnhA.png https://image.prntscr.com/image/v3TZLQpwQZ6ruJ1pewXSig.png  Phase 1 Development 2015-2016  Website development started 2015  Android app development Started 2016 iOS app development started  Phase 2 Crowd Funding Late 2017 to Early 2018 November 15 to December 13, 2017 Token Pre-Sale  January 1 to January 28, 2018 Main ICO  February 2018 Classy Coin start trading in major decentralized exchanges  February 2018 Hire 6 more developers and 2 designer and increase our development team to 8 developers and 3 designers.  Phase 3 Launching the Network 2018 Q2-2019 Q2 2018 The release of Classy Social Network website  Q2 2018 The release of iOS app (beta version)  Q2 2018 The release of android app (beta version)  Q3 2018 The release of full website  Q3 2018 The release of full iOs app  Q3 2018 The release of full android app  Q3 2018 Classy Coin is fully integrated as a payment method on Classy Social Network  Q3 2018 Hotel Booking functionality is fully implemented in Classy Social Network  Q3 2018 Flight booking functionality is fully implemented in Classy Social Network  Q3 2018 Car Hire services is fully implemented in Classy social networking platform  Q3 2018 Listings services is fully implemented in Classy social network platform.  Q4 2018 The release of iOS and android VPN application   Important Contract Information Name: ClassyCoin Symbol: ClassyCoin Decimals:16 Contract Address: 0x30cc0e266cf33b8eac6a99cbd98e39b890cfd69b Maximum Supply (hard cap) - 100,000,000 ClassyCoin Emission rate - No new coins will ever be created Role of Coin/Token - used to buy Goods, Services and Ad spaces on Classy Network Available for puchase-70,000,000 ClassyCoin   ICO INFORMATION Accepted Currency - ETH Only Minimum Transaction Amount - 0.1 ETH Pre-ICO Sale Period - 00:00am GMT November 15th 2017 to 00:00m GMT Dec 13th 2017 Main ICO Sale Period - 00:00am GMT Jan 1st 2018 to 00:00m GMT Jan 28th 2018 Coin Distribution - Contract will distribute coins/tokens instantly upon receiving ETH Minimum Goal - 1,000,000 ClassyCoin If minimum not met, refund will be issued via the Smart Contract  Official Links Website: http://www.classycoin.io Telegram: https://t.me/joinchat/E7bGkULR97-OrNjgT7QaMQ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ClassyCoinCurrency/ Twitter: https://twitter.com/classycoin [/quote]

Author: Pivooooo
Title: ClassyCoin
Body: There are a lot of projects with social networks now! And you have to work hard to win competition! Imagine a fully decentralized social network, where all the data and content is stored on the blockchain instead of centralized servers, and all the power lies with the users; not some individual nerd or company. Classy Network is one such step in the direction to get the users a platform that is not only powered by them but actually owned by them. It is the new generation decentralized social networking platform which is based on the ethereum blockchain for global connectivity and community building. Classy Network integrates peer to peer payment system and end to end fully encrypted features with no possibility of third party control of the data and zero possibility of downtime. Being an on-chain platform (Blockchain based), all of the user content would be lying on the blockchain instead of centralized servers. The platform allows you to communicate with friends and family in multiple unique ways, while providing state-of-the-art security and privacy.

The coin is intended to be used within Classy Network to buy ad spaces, pay for goods and services and give tips to friends and families across the Classy Network. At Classy Network, we believe in supporting community building and social interaction with cryptocurrency rewards. For inspiring participation in the community, ClassyCoin would be presenting the users with a currency or a free market economy that is a fair accounting system, and consistently reflects each person's contribution. ClassyCoin aims to accurately and transparently reward an unbounded number of individuals who make subjective contributions to its community. We are taking appropriate steps to give people a real alternative and choice to connect with their loves one and be in full control of their data. Considering that, we have taken a revolutionary step of creating a blockchain based social networking platform.   Background  Social media have become ubiquitous and are playing an increasingly critical role in society. The wide use of social media platforms has generated massive user generated contents (UGCs). Research reveals that there are 2.5 billion active users of social networking sites, who collectively generate content having worth more than billions of dollars‚Äô. ClassyCoin is created based on idea of supporting social media and online communities by returning much of its value to the people who provide valuable contributions by rewarding them with cryptocurrency, and through this process create a currency that is able to reach a broad market, including people who have yet to participate in any cryptocurrency economy.   Introduction to Classy Social Network  Imagine a fully decentralized social network, where all the data and content is stored on the blockchain instead of centralized servers, and all the power lies with the users; not some individual nerd or company. Classy Network is one such step in the direction to get the users a platform that is not only powered by them but actually owned by them. It is the new generation decentralized social networking platform which is based on the ethereum blockchain for global connectivity and community building. Classy Network integrates peer to peer payment system and end to end fully encrypted features with no possibility of third party control of the data and zero possibility of downtime. Being an on-chain platform (Blockchain based), all of the user content would be lying on the blockchain instead of centralized servers. The platform allows you to communicate with friends and family in multiple unique ways, while providing state-of-the-art security and privacy.   Classy Network is backed by ClassyCoin- a cryptocurrency designed to be used for buying goods and services, purchase ad spaces from the integrated ad platform, donating to crowd funding campaigns, giving tips to friends and families across the network. Here is a brief description of the features that would be integrated into the Classy Network and would change your perception of what can be achieved through social media networks.  Classy Social Network Functionalities  1.VPN Social App Classy Network will be powered by a special VPN Social app. The app will facilitate both the mobile version of the network and also the desktop version to offer extreme browsing privacy. 2.YouTube integrated Classy Network would come with YouTube integrated which is the world‚Äôs biggest video sharing platform. This way users would be able to not only view the billions of video available directly in their feed but share them as well and get a fair reward for each impression, view and click.   Besides, this would also enable the network to avoid glitches being faced in the video content e.g. the current glitch of getting the app hanged while a video is being played on facebook.   3.Peer to Peer Payment Peer-to-peer payment system are electronic money transfers made from one person to another through an intermediary, typically referred to as a P2P payment application. P2P payments can be sent and received via mobile device or any home computer with access to the Internet, offering a convenient alternative to traditional payment methods. Classy Network has the built in functionality of peer to peer payment that would facilitates the users to send and receive their earned amount directly into their e-wallets without having to worry about massive surcharges implemented on traditional payment methods. 4.Marketplace Integrated Classy Network incorporates all of the e-commerce functions. It will allow you to create product Post for a specific product or service. Your friends, family or followers would see your post and would be able to purchase or bit directly. 5.Classy Network Mobile Apps Classy Network will be available both in the iOS and Android version. The mobile apps are being designed in a manner to support all features of the web version as well. Users would be able to chat, post, share, like and gets real time notification.   6.Instant Hollywood News and Updates For all Cinema lovers out there, Classy Network would allow you to get the latest updates from the world of Hollywood instantly. You would be able to watch and share videos related to Hollywood and keep yourself updated about the newest trends in the world of fashion. 7.News Publisher The Classy Network also comes integrated with the custom functionality of supporting news publishing. You would be able to view, publish and share news instantly and keep updated about whatever interest you have. 8.Listings Service Classy Network sports a listing service with the aim to provide accurate and structured data about properties for sale. The listing service would maintain a mechanism for listing brokers to offer compensation to buyer brokers who bring a buyer for their listed property without any service fee. 9.Personalized blog Instead of creating a separate blog on sites such as Wordpress.com or other, ClassyCoin comes integrated with Personalized Blog functionality. Unlike the current social networking platforms which mainly provide users with the facility of posts, Classy Network let the user create a personalized blog supported by a variety of custom functionalities such as different fonts and custom designs. The user also has the facility to view, like and share other users‚Äô blogs as well.   10.Complete Decentralized On-Chain Classy Network would be a completely decentralized on-chain platform that would allow users not to worry about a single centralized authority controlling the entire network. Instead it will be the community who will be the actual owner of the platform. All of the application data, user data and multimedia uploads will be stored on the blockchain. 11.Privacy Classy Network is a community driver project whose main focus is the privacy of our community and its data. Powered by ethereum smart contract blockchain technology, all of the data is distributed on a ledger without any single point of focus or failure.  Every single feature inside the network is end to end fully encrypted, which make it impossible for any third party to access your data.
